       4,
       "functools.cached_property.__class__.__name__.__len__() == 4 — 'type' has 4 characters: t-y-p-e; str.__len__() returns 4; verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra198"]
    - [cachedprop_init_qualname_eq,
