       "functools.cached_property.__init__.__qualname__.__eq__('cached_property.__init__') == True — __init__ is a method of cached_property so its qualname carries the class prefix; __qualname__ is 'cached_property.__init__' (len=24); str.__eq__('cached_property.__init__') returns True; verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra198"]
    - [cachedprop_init_qualname_len,
       cached_property.__init__.__qualname__.__len__,
       [],
       24,
       "functools.cached_property.__init__.__qualname__.__len__() == 24 — 'cached_property.__init__' has 24 characters; str.__len__() returns 24; verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra198"]
