       "functools.cached_property.__set_name__.__qualname__.__len__() == 28 — 'cached_property.__set_name__' has 28 characters; str.__len__() returns 28; verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra198"]
    - [cachedprop_doc_class_name_eq,
