       "functools.cached_property.__doc__.__class__.__name__.__eq__('NoneType') == True — cached_property has no docstring in Python 3.14 so __doc__ is None; None.__class__.__name__ is 'NoneType' (len=8); str.__eq__('NoneType') returns True; verified with Python 3.14.3; new to extra198"]
    - [cachedprop_doc_class_name_len,
       cached_property.__doc__.__class__.__name__.__len__,
